Refactor and extend Scylla integration.
Replace `EventExecutor` with `Executor` for flexibility in `EventBus`. Add and implement Scylla-related utilities, including repository, query executors, schema management, and validation tools to enhance database functionality. Introduce `dependabot.yml` for dependency management.

Refactor scheduler framework and simplify implementation
Replaced heavily redundant scheduler classes with streamlined utilities and an enum-based approach for thread handling. Removed unused implementations, added a SchedulerUtils helper class, and introduced better integration with external APIs. These changes improve maintainability and reduce complexity in the codebase.
Created new branch master in mikeamiry/balanclava
